Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:09.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「Carry on and burn it down」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:12.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「you've got to be the one you want」
